We've Got You Covered
Perfect Installs
Your roof is your home's main defense against the elements. Let us walk you through the best options to fit your needs and once you feel comfortable with your choice, we'll handle the complete installation.

Your Home is Importantâ€‹
It contains the most important thing in the world.  Your Family.  We believe you and your family only deserve the best and that is why we only install Armadura Metal Roofs.  We believe in Canada and Armadura is made in Canada by Canadians.

Certified Installers
All of our installers are trained for working at heights, covered by WSIB and certified by the manufacturer as Master Installers.
